com.github.baniuk.ImageJTestSuite.dataaccess

Class DataLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.baniuk.ImageJTestSuite.dataaccess.DataLoader

  • public class DataLoader
extends Object
    Minimalistic test data loader.

    Load list of points saved as one-column list with interleaving coordinates of vertices: 

     x1
 y1
 x2
 y2
 ...
 ...
 xn
 yn

    The file must contain even number of data. Exemplary code in Matlab to create such file: TODO add example

    Author:
    p.baniukiewicz
